json.name: Test Integration Dashboard
json.description: A comprehensive test dashboard for integration testing with various panel types and data sources

json.name: Response Times by Dimension
json.description: Grafana panel 'Response Times by Dimension' in dashboard 'Test Integration Dashboard' using datasource test-postgres

json.viewLogic:
SELECT
  time,
  value,
  dimension
FROM test_metrics
WHERE
  metric = 'response_time' AND time > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL '1 HOUR'
ORDER BY
  time ASC

json.name: Recent Metrics
json.description: Grafana panel 'Recent Metrics' in dashboard 'Test Integration Dashboard' using datasource test-postgres

json.viewLogic:
SELECT
  time,
  metric,
  value,
  dimension
FROM test_metrics
WHERE
  time > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL '1 HOUR'
ORDER BY
  time DESC
LIMIT 10

json.name: Total Metrics Count
json.description: Grafana panel 'Total Metrics Count' in dashboard 'Test Integration Dashboard' using datasource test-postgres

json.viewLogic:
SELECT
  COUNT(*) AS count
FROM test_metrics
WHERE
  time > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL '1 HOUR'
